OL,3,CWarren Gatland stays for 2025 Six
OL,4,CNations but WRU director to resign
OL,6,FThe Welsh Rugby Union (WRU) has
OL,7,Fannounced that Warren Gatland will
OL,8,Fstay as head coach of the men's
OL,9,Fnational team for the 2025 Six Nations
OL,10,Fcampaign, however the WRU's Executive
OL,11,FDirector Nigel Walker will step down.
OL,13,FThe news comes following a review of
OL,14,Fthe squad's performance under
OL,15,FGatland's second tenure in charge.
OL,16,FLast month the team suffered a record-
OL,17,Fbreaking 12th consecutive defeat,
OL,18,Fleaving the team without a test match
OL,19,Fwin this year.
