OL,6,FIn a statement, the WRU said its board
OL,7,Fhad "seriously considered wholesale
OL,8,Fimmediate change" but instead decided
OL,9,Fthat "challenging" Gatland to turn
OL,10,Faround the fortunes of the team on the
OL,11,Fpitch was the best way forward.
OL,13,FHowever the Union's Executive Director
OL,14,Fof Rugby Walker has announced he is
OL,15,Fresigning, after joining the WRU in
OL,16,F2021.
OL,18,FWalker said he had not taken the
OL,19,Fdecision lightly but it was "time for
OL,20,Fa new leader for the performance
OL,21,Fdepartment".
