OL,6,FThe review of the squad's performance
OL,7,Fover the past 12 months, carried out
OL,8,Fby WRU CEO Abi Tierney, also gave
OL,9,Fseveral recommendations.
OL,11,FOne of which was the appointment of a
OL,12,Fnew high-performance advisory panel
OL,13,Fthat will be up and running in the New
OL,14,FYear and include former senior
OL,15,Fplayers. The CEO will also review the
OL,16,Fhigh-performance structure at the WRU
OL,17,Fand "make necessary changes".
