OL,6,FA third recommendation was that the
OL,7,FWRU will immediately consider
OL,8,Fintroducing additional personnel
OL,9,Fassisting Gatland, with the aim of
OL,10,F"improving mindset, mentality and
OL,11,Fculture within the squad". Changes are
OL,12,Fplanned before the 2025 tournament,
OL,13,Fincluding improving mentoring support
OL,14,Ffor players.
OL,16,FTierney, who completes her first year
OL,17,Fin charge in January, said another
OL,18,Fassessment of performances will follow
OL,19,Fthe 2025 Championship.
