OL,6,FShe said: "I have had a number of very
OL,7,Fhonest conversations with Warren and I
OL,8,Fwill make no secret of the fact that
OL,9,Fhis position was on the line as we
OL,10,Fundertook our review.
OL,12,F"Further than that, like any head
OL,13,Fcoach in any sport, he knows the
OL,14,Fsecurity of his position is directly
OL,15,Frelated to the performances of the
OL,16,Fteam and that this is a situation that
OL,17,Fwill continue to intensify.
