OL,6,F"I am pleased to have the support of
OL,7,FAbi and the Board to take the squad
OL,8,Finto the Six Nations. This group of
OL,9,Fplayers has a huge amount of potential
OL,10,Fand we will be working incredibly hard
OL,11,Ftogether to turnaround our fortunes on
OL,12,Fthe pitch. We know, more than ever, we
OL,13,Fwill be judged on competitiveness, on
OL,14,Fsuccess and on winning during the 2025
OL,15,Fcampaign.
