OL,6,F"During the review I had the
OL,7,Fopportunity to explain my thinking,
OL,8,Fbut I also appreciate the feedback and
OL,9,Fconstructive challenge that has been
OL,10,Fput to me. I'd like to thank the
OL,11,Fplayers in particular for their
OL,12,Finvolvement and their honesty. I am
OL,13,Flooking forward to the challenge
OL,14,Fahead."
OL,16,FMeanwhile, Huw Bevan, who is currently
OL,17,Finterim performance director, and
OL,18,Fcommunity director, Geraint John, will
OL,19,Ftake on Nigel Walker's executive
OL,20,Fduties in the short term following the
OL,21,Fannouncement that he is resigning.
