OL,6,FIn the New Year the WRU will look to
OL,7,Frecruit a new Director of Professional
OL,8,FRugby.
OL,10,FWalker joined the Welsh Rugby Union in
OL,11,F2021 as performance director and
OL,12,Fintroduced the first professional
OL,13,Fcontracts for Wales Women later that
OL,14,Fyear. He took on the interim chief
OL,15,Fexecutive role in January 2023 and
OL,16,Freverted to his current role with the
OL,17,Farrival of CEO Abi Tierney in January
OL,18,F2024.
