OL,6,FBut 2024 has been a difficult year for
OL,7,FWalker. He was at the heart of a
OL,8,Fbreakdown in relationship between the
OL,9,FUnion and the senior women's squad
OL,10,Fwhen contract negotiations descended
OL,11,Finto chaos this summer.
OL,13,F"This decision has not been made
OL,14,Flightly as I have cherished my time at
OL,15,Fthe Welsh Rugby Union immensely, but
OL,16,Fit's time for a new leader for the
OL,17,Fperformance department," said Walker.
