OL,6,F"My tenure has not been without its
OL,7,Fchallenges and we have achieved a
OL,8,Fgreat amount but, ultimately, it is
OL,9,Fright that I am judged on performances
OL,10,Fon the pitch and both of our senior
OL,11,Fteams have found the last 12 months
OL,12,Fextremely difficult and therefore I
OL,13,Fbelieve now is the right time for me
OL,14,Fto step down.
