OL,6,F"I am proud of my achievements in the
OL,7,Frole and as interim CEO through a
OL,8,Fdifficult period of time for the Welsh
OL,9,FRugby Union. I thank all those who I
OL,10,Fhave worked alongside during that time
OL,11,Fand would like to pay special mention
OL,12,Fin gratitude to our former chair Ieuan
OL,13,FEvans, and, to wish our current chair
OL,14,FRichard Collier-Keywood and our CEO
OL,15,FAbi Tierney much success in the
OL,16,Ffuture."
OL,18,FTierney said Walker has spearheaded
OL,19,Fsignificant achievements for Welsh
OL,20,FRugby and thanked him for all he had
OL,21,Fdone.
